targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  test_id,protocol,num_streams,duration,reverse
FROM iperf3_start_test_start
order by test_id desc limit 1;

SELECT
  test_time,test_name, test_user, iperf3_client, iperf3_server,test_runs, args, test_complete
FROM iperf3_general_info
order by test_id desc limit 1;

SELECT
  UNIX_TIMESTAMP(time) as time_sec,
  bigint(bits_per_second) as value,
  
FROM iperf3_intervals_stream
WHERE $__timeFilter(time_column)
ORDER BY <time_column> ASC

select bits_per_second from iperf3_end_sum

WHERE type="sum_sent" and test_id=(select test_id from iperf3_general_info order by test_id desc limit 1)

select bits_per_second from iperf3_end_sum

WHERE type="sum_sent" and test_id=(select test_id from iperf3_general_info order by test_id desc limit 1)

select bits_per_second from iperf3_end_sum

WHERE type="sum_sent" and test_id=(select test_id from iperf3_general_info order by test_id desc limit 1)
